Populate Go build info metadata in go_binary with dependency versions.

This ports the internal BuildInfo feature into the vendored Orchestrion fork. The port keeps the buildinfo aspect, linker metadata plumbing, builder-side modinfo generation, and runtime test coverage, but it also adds the explicit rules_license dependency wiring this fork needs locally for both Bzlmod and WORKSPACE consumers.

The local tests do not rely on downstream Gazelle metadata generation. Instead they synthesize PackageInfo directly with rules_license package_info targets so the external-version path is validated inside this repository.

